data.title: 21 fun facts for October, 28 (+3 bonus) - Historical events, discover what happened on this day.
data.meta_description: October 28th holds numerous historical and cultural milestones worldwide, such as the dedication of the Statue of Liberty, the founding of Harvard University, and the birth of Bill Gates. It's also a day of celebration, including events like International Animation Day, Plush Animal Lover's Day, and National Chocolate Day.
